General
* do a code walk to weed out anything that breaks thread-safety
* produce a validation testing framework that is invokable from ant
* produce a performance testing framework that is invokable from ant
* make stack trace location reporting more accurate and meaningful
* reorganize code into new directory structure

Features
* implement binary ports
* port scsh's SREs
* add type and object system that is tightly integrated with S2J
* write a debugger
* add mechanism for dynamic loading of scheme modules
* add support for loading pre-expanded and pre-compiled modules
* rationalize/integrate modules, libraries, slib
* framework for doing source-level optimizations that are automatically
  rolled back when assumptions are invalidated.
